Made on Sep 2024 by Sunmyoung Yun
Simple game project made with C++ & SFML
recreated chrome dinosaur game

--------------------------------------------------------- How to open 
1. Copy repo in VScode
2. Type "make" in terminal to compile
3. Type ./ASAtut in terminal to run game 

--------------------------------------------------------- Game play
    - Press B to restart Game

    - Press W to move player up
    - Press S to move player down
    - Press space bar to jump
    - Click on screen to launch a bullet 

